{"tid":946354,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"（A/I) 第七史詩 Epic Seven (32)個個都有暗拳","createTime":"2018-12-18T12:49:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T12:51:23.000Z","uid":12359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1db4da61c4b589d3d6c6006da29b5d8471b02d18","tid":946354,"uid":12359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T12:49:18.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>廠商</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">世曼凱代理<br />\nSuper Creative 開發</span> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JUp9Nm7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJUp9Nm7.png&h=7a32ea27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>三個SER</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1. Korea Server(已於8月30日開服)</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Asia Server(預計11月8日全新開張)</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3. Global Server(預計11月8日全新開張)</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xud27nu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXud27nu.jpg&h=475b57cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Wap8QJ7xi9Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWap8QJ7xi9Y&d=snKWCexEeILdzeybrFNHlP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=736c9136\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Wap8QJ7xi9Y</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">巴打照顧區</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dPTyuD5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdPTyuD5.jpg&h=2d64cf50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bdvQwSr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-