9ec2649f7bbfb","tid":946354,"uid":12359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T12:50:27.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">新手入門 - 首抽抽乜篇<br />\n(By 薯丸)18/11/11</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n5星就專注木奶先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，有佢+啲3星都夠過10-10<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oST7kdx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoST7kdx.jpg&h=52a64e5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果抽唔到5星木奶，有以下兩隻4星火奶/水奶都可以一戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽聞火奶係應用上仲好過木奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9ffah0M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9ffah0M.jpg&h=f684d9d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kqRgX0N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkqRgX0N.jpg&h=e0733484&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好用嘅盾就5星水盾一隻(男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7uFhHsK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7uFhHsK.jpg&h=398396a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4星木盾一隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z5Kuyzq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz5Kuyzq.jpg&h=b61f1862&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3星三戰神<br />\n<br />\n一：毒弓玩%數<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，靠佢毒鳩死晒ON9BOSS<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cocWX1P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcocWX1P.jpg&h=446786f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n二：火爪，極似LOL Annie<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 4攻2暴，簡單暴力<br />\n畀你見識咩叫3星&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;5星<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jS3GpHa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjS3GpHa.jpg&h=ac92d6ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三：暗槍(強烈懷疑人設條友睇過鬼父<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n依隻普池唔會抽到嘅，同埋靠任務可以取得，見啲大佬介紹又係3星正嘢，同技能有動畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LkbMAP7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLkbMAP7.jpg&h=825f660a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5OJbMWN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5OJbMWN.jpg&h=73bada87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n基本上我講嘅都係好表面，想深入了解可以以下網站了解更多<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/A.php?bsn=34880\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FA.php%3Fbsn%3D34880&d=snKWCexEeILdzeybrFNHlP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=cf8a0ad5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/A.php?bsn=34880</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://epic7.game100.wiki/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fepic7.game100.wiki%2F&d=snKWCexEeILdzeybrFNHlP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=913b0922\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://epic7.game100.wiki/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </div><br />\n\f"},{"pid":"ae4dddf1de36a956a1205d44ceb512a628b71e1e","tid":946354,"uid":12359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T12:51:23.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">新手入門 - 首抽點抽篇<br />\n(By 薯丸)18/11/11</span></strong></span><br />\n抽抽分兩種，問下自己想刷單5星定多5星先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果只係單5星嘅，請睇<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">300抽</span></strong></span><br />\n(單5星開波就唔使頭七抽，直接到1-10玩300抽，因為單抽100石，儲夠950可以換十次單抽+送3隻企鵝你咬下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">300抽</span></strong></span><br />\n完咗1-10會畀你任你抽30次10連<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ga19kx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ga19kx.jpg&h=663dca12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/02bQidU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F02bQidU.jpg&h=d5af5acb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n抽完後<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7M9FFve.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7M9FFve.jpg&h=5e6f1727&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔啱就繼續【??/30 再度召喚】，而??就係你抽嘅第幾次<br />\n啱嘅就右邊【確定召喚】，鎖咗就無得再抽<br />\n但你撳完之後系統都會再問多你一次，所以睇清楚唔怕撳錯<br />\n<br />\n如果你唔肯定係洗定鎖，可以撳左下角返回出返去，唔使怕系統洗咗<br />\n因為只要你一日未鎖同未洗，佢都會KEEP返依十抽嘅結果畀你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好運起上嚟300抽會中到木奶，但衰起上嚟可以0五星<br />\n到最後30/30嘅時候，你唔會再有得洗，因為只會得返鎖依個結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xLaQ2J8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxLaQ2J8.jpg&h=d0ea802c&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"}]}